description: After Screamin’ Wiener won over the hearts of Carmel with their delicious hot dogs and sausages smothered in specialty toppings, they’re cartin’ into the Indy scene and providing brand new fans their tasty handheld cuisine. Keep an eye out for Screamin’ Wiener on the streets if you want to give these delicious treats a try. If you’ve got a party coming up, Screamin’ Wiener has scrumptious tacos, sandwiches, and Italian entrees too that your guests will absolutely love.
name: Screamin' Wiener
